<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class= title>
          <h1 class= text-center >Refugee talk</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="connect text-center">
          <h2>CONNECT</h2>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras euismod sapien lacus, varius suscipit orci
          posuere vitae. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae;
          Phasellus sit amet feugiat augue. Donec turpis sapien, sagittis sit amet mattis id, interdum sit amet lectus.
          Pellentesque venenatis lectus leo, id porttitor erat feugiat et. Nullam auctor leo eu nibh pulvinar euismod. Etiam iaculis varius
          ultrices. Nulla bibendum mauris quis velit finibus, sed venenatis.
        </div>
        <div class="button-center">
          <% if signed_in? %>
          <% else %>
          <%= link_to(new_user_registration_path) do  %>
          <div class="btn sign-in-button">
            SIGN UP
          </div>
          <% end  %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="dutchy-list">
          <hr>
          <h2 class="text-center">
            THE DUTCHIES
          </h2>
          <div class="dutchies">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">
                <% @dutchies.first(6).each do |dutchie| %>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                  <div class= "card">
                    <div class= 'card-photo'>
                      <%= image_tag(dutchie.photo, class: 'avatar-large')  %>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <div class='card-name'>
                        <%= dutchie.username %> 
                      </div>
                      <div class="card-description">
                        <%= dutchie.description %> 
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <%= link_to "", dutchy_path(dutchie), class: 'card-link'  %>    
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center">
        <%=link_to "ALL DUTCHIES", dutchies_path, class:"btn dutchy-button" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>


